      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be verified under a documented SQA plan with version control and regression testing.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is used under an ISO 9001-compliant SQA framework. Version control, regression test suite, and release notes are documented. Achieved level meets MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
