      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence closure and Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model are established for rotary blood pump CFD. Formal model-form uncertainty analysis is beyond MRL 2 requirements and is scoped out."
    },
    {
