      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity to input parameter uncertainty not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Fluid viscosity and density are taken from established literature values for bovine blood at 37°C. Formal input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2 and is scoped out of this assessment."
